cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with video summarization, which is a common task in computer vision. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with both edited and raw videos, which are common multimedia formats. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possibility as video summarization can be seen as a form of information retrieval. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also possible as the paper mentions learning the weights of the models in a supervised manner. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with summarizing the storyline of a video, which can be seen as a form of natural language processing.
